## The non-negotiables

- Plan mode is required for changes touching more than 3 files, public APIs, refactors, or migrations.
- No placeholder comments. Ask if you do not have enough context.
- Use the project's package manager (`<pkg-mgr>`).
- Run the fast verification after every meaningful change.

